--- API Configuration ---

The port the server will listen on

PORT=8080

A strong, random string used to sign JWT tokens.

Do not share this in production!

JWT_SECRET=your-super-secret-staff-level-key-change-me

--- Database Configuration (PostgreSQL) ---

Format: postgres://<user>:<password>@<host>:<port>/<db_name>?sslmode=disable

Use 'localhost' for local development or 'sentinel-db' if running inside Docker Compose

DB_URL=postgres://user:password@localhost:5432/sentinel?sslmode=disable

--- Cache Configuration (Redis) ---

Format: <host>:<port>

Use 'localhost' for local development or 'sentinel-cache' if running inside Docker Compose

REDIS_URL=localhost:6379

--- Argon2id Tuning (Optional) ---

These values can be overridden to adjust security/performance trade-offs

HASH_MEMORY=65536

HASH_ITERATIONS=3

HASH_PARALLELISM=2